WEBVTT

00:05.244 --> 00:07.516
<i>PREVIOUSLY ON "WEEDS"...</i>

00:07.549 --> 00:10.420
THIS IS YOUR NEW JOB.
IT'S A MATERNITY STORE.

00:10.454 --> 00:12.526
THIS IS THE BACK ROOM.

00:14.663 --> 00:16.366
YOU STAY. NO ENTRA AQUí.
OKAY?

00:19.438 --> 00:22.478
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS
IN SPANISH ]

00:22.512 --> 00:23.881
iDíGAME, PENDEJA!

00:23.915 --> 00:26.052
YOU MUST BE PUNISHED.

00:27.756 --> 00:29.225
Nancy:
HE'S THE MAYOR?

00:32.464 --> 00:34.803
ARE YOU IN LOVE WITH ME?
YES.

00:34.836 --> 00:37.274
MOM?

00:37.308 --> 00:39.913
YOU TAKE TOO MANY DRUGS.
MOSTLY XANAX AND COKE.

00:39.947 --> 00:42.284
COCAINE? COCA?

00:47.161 --> 00:48.396
AT SOME POINT RECENTLY,

00:48.430 --> 00:50.535
EVERYTHING
BECAME RIGHT OR WRONG.

00:50.568 --> 00:51.604
WHAT DID YOU DO?

00:53.340 --> 00:55.878
WHAT THE FUCK?
Nancy:
EXACTLY! WHAT THE FUCK?!

00:55.912 --> 00:57.147
THIS IS SUPPOSED TO BE
A POT TUNNEL!

00:57.181 --> 00:59.720
THERE'S NO MAGICAL "WEED ONLY"
SIGN AT THE ENTRANCE.

00:59.753 --> 01:01.824
CAPTAIN TILL,
THERE'S A TUNNEL.

01:01.857 --> 01:04.328
YOU MAKE A BUST,
YOU GET GUILLERMO,

01:04.362 --> 01:05.464
AND IT NEVER
COMES BACK TO ME.

01:05.497 --> 01:07.602
I'M SIMONE.
DO YOU PARTY?
I'M HARMONY.

01:07.636 --> 01:08.336
YEAH.

01:08.370 --> 01:10.207
HEAD‐CHEESE SANDWICH,
PLEASE.

01:10.240 --> 01:12.579
I'M NOT GIVING WEED
TO MY LITTLE BROTHER.
OH.

01:14.850 --> 01:15.919
YOU'RE IN LOVE WITH NANCY.

01:15.952 --> 01:17.187
I'M NOT IN LOVE
WITH NANCY.

01:17.221 --> 01:19.158
YOU SO ARE.
I GOT TO GO.

01:19.191 --> 01:20.360
SHIT'S BLOWING UP.
I USED TO HAVE SHIT ‐‐

01:20.394 --> 01:22.431
USED TO BLOW UP ALL THE TIME ‐‐
NOW NOTHING.

01:23.634 --> 01:25.337
LEGENDARY!

01:25.370 --> 01:30.447
I AM THE ONLY ONE HERE THAT
HAS ANY CHANCE TO MAKE AMENDS.

01:30.480 --> 01:32.351
I DON'T KNOW
WHERE QUINN IS.

01:32.384 --> 01:34.455
SHE'S LIVING IN OAXACA
WITH A GUY NAMED RODOLFO.

01:34.488 --> 01:36.727
Quinn: I'M JUST SO GLAD
THAT YOU CAME HERE TO SEE ME

01:36.760 --> 01:38.396
SO THAT I COULD TIE YOU UP
AND LOCK YOU IN A ROOM

01:38.430 --> 01:41.737
UNTIL I SELL YOUR ASS
BACK INTO SUBURBAN SLAVERY,

01:41.770 --> 01:43.874
YOU FUCKING BITCH.

01:43.908 --> 01:44.910
SHALL I CALL
YOUR FATHER NOW?

01:44.943 --> 01:47.582
TELL DADDY DEAN
I WANT $200,000.

01:47.616 --> 01:48.350
WHO'S GUILLERMO'S BOSS?

01:48.383 --> 01:51.189
WHO OWNS
THE FUCKING TUNNEL?!

01:51.222 --> 01:52.391
I‐I DON'T KNOW.

01:52.424 --> 01:53.628
I'D LIKE TO SEE YOU
TONIGHT.

01:53.661 --> 01:55.063
HAS TO BE TONIGHT?

01:55.097 --> 01:56.199
I WILL SEND A CAR.

01:56.232 --> 01:57.434
I CAN DRIVE MYSELF.

01:57.468 --> 01:58.704
Woman:
Terrifically Gift Baskets.

01:58.738 --> 02:02.044
I NEED TO GET A BIRTHDAY GIFT
FOR MY 18‐YEAR‐OLD.

02:02.077 --> 02:03.046
CAN YOU HELP ME?

02:03.079 --> 02:04.482
I'M THINKING
OF BUYING SOME LAND.

02:04.516 --> 02:07.021
A LITTLE FARM
WHERE I CAN GROW POT.
YOU WANT A PARTNER?

02:07.054 --> 02:08.691
Woman: What would you like
the card to say?

02:08.724 --> 02:11.630
"SILAS, YOU ARE LOVED."
AND ADD THE BUTTER COOKIES.

02:11.664 --> 02:13.601
I THOUGHT YOU LOVED ME.

02:13.634 --> 02:17.174
I DO LOVE YOU.
I THINK I CAN MAKE YOU HAPPY.

02:17.207 --> 02:19.613
IT'S TOO LATE.

02:24.723 --> 02:27.061
FEELS LIKE A BOY.

02:27.094 --> 02:29.599
[ SIGHS ]

02:29.633 --> 02:31.904
[ SIGHS ]

02:31.937 --> 02:35.143
[ MONITOR BEEPING ]

02:43.861 --> 02:46.600
[ SIGHS ]

02:54.015 --> 02:57.488
IT FEELS LIKE A BOY.

03:12.652 --> 03:15.190
[ GUNSHOTS ]

03:18.597 --> 03:21.704
ANYONE ELSE
KNOW ABOUT THE SITUATION?

03:25.812 --> 03:27.247
OKAY.

03:27.281 --> 03:30.755
WELL, SEND SOME FLOWERS
TO THE FAMILIES, AND, UH...

03:30.788 --> 03:32.124
BUY A NEW RUG.

03:32.157 --> 03:34.161
UM...

03:34.195 --> 03:35.765
YOU SHOULD GO HOME NOW.

03:35.798 --> 03:37.769
I SHOULD.

03:37.802 --> 03:38.938
CESAR WILL TAKE YOU HOME.

03:38.971 --> 03:41.510
NO, THAT'S OKAY. I HAVE MY CAR.
I CAN DRIVE MYSELF.

03:41.543 --> 03:44.482
CESAR WILL DRIVE YOU HOME
IN YOUR CAR, THEN.

03:44.516 --> 03:47.488
NO, HE MUST HAVE
A LOT ON HIS MIND.

03:47.522 --> 03:50.494
THE SUDDEN DEATH OF TWO...
WORK FRIENDS.

03:50.528 --> 03:52.297
HE SHOULD TAKE SOME TIME
TO PROCESS.

03:52.331 --> 03:54.135
I DON'T
NEED TO PROCESS.

03:54.168 --> 03:55.838
OH.

03:57.107 --> 03:59.412
IF YOU'RE GONNA KILL ME,
PLEASE DO IT FAST,

03:59.445 --> 04:00.548
LIKE WITH THESE GUYS,

04:00.581 --> 04:02.451
NOT THE WHOLE,
"OH, LET'S GO FOR A DRIVE,

04:02.484 --> 04:05.490
AND THEN AT SOME POINT, WE'LL
PULL OVER AND I'LL SHOOT YOU."

04:05.525 --> 04:06.660
NANCY.

04:06.693 --> 04:07.829
[ SIGHS ]

04:07.862 --> 04:08.864
GO HOME.

04:08.898 --> 04:11.637
ALONE?

04:11.670 --> 04:12.705
YES.

04:13.707 --> 04:16.780
I WILL BE IN TOUCH.

04:19.653 --> 04:20.788
UH...

04:20.822 --> 04:22.124
THERE'S ANOTHER DOOR.

04:22.157 --> 04:23.727
OH, RIGHT, THE OTHER DOOR.
OKAY.

04:25.130 --> 04:26.533
I'LL TALK TO YOU SOON.

04:26.567 --> 04:27.401
OH, YES.

04:27.434 --> 04:30.440
OKAY. BYE, THEN.

04:33.279 --> 04:35.283
[ SIGHS ]

04:35.317 --> 04:37.822
THIS IS A BEAUTIFUL CARD.

04:37.856 --> 04:39.926
HERE. TAKE IT.

04:39.960 --> 04:41.964
I THINK I'M GONNA PASS.

04:41.997 --> 04:44.301
BEAUTY IS SUBJECTIVE.

04:44.335 --> 04:46.472
HOWEVER,
THIS IS GORGEOUS.

04:46.507 --> 04:48.878
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

04:48.911 --> 04:50.347
YELLO?

04:50.380 --> 04:54.155
IS THIS DEAN HODES?
MR. DEAN HODES?

04:54.188 --> 04:55.625
DAMN IT!

04:55.658 --> 04:56.693
What?

04:56.727 --> 04:57.662
FUCKING BUGS.

04:57.695 --> 05:00.902
Please be quiet
when I'm on the phone!

05:00.935 --> 05:04.375
Dean:
Hello? Who is this?

05:04.408 --> 05:05.845
I HAVE YOUR WIFE.

05:05.878 --> 05:07.549
EXCUSE ME?
Celia.

05:07.582 --> 05:09.619
I HAVE YOUR WIFE ‐‐
CELIA.

05:09.653 --> 05:12.892
NOW, YOU LISTEN TO ME.
YOU SEND ME MONEY.

05:12.926 --> 05:15.765
UH, YEAH, SHE'S NO LONGER
MY WIFE. WE'RE DIVORCED.

05:15.798 --> 05:17.569
THEN I WILL KILL HER.

05:17.602 --> 05:20.340
YOU HEAR ME?
IF YOU DO NOT PAY, SHE DIES.

05:20.373 --> 05:21.543
DAD, I'M THROWING A 6.

05:21.577 --> 05:23.647
UH, YEAH, LISTEN, I'M BROKE,
AND SHE'S MY EX,

05:23.681 --> 05:25.585
SO YOU DO
WHAT YOU GOT TO DO, OKAY?

05:25.618 --> 05:26.920
ARE YOU NOT LISTENING
TO ME?

05:26.954 --> 05:28.122
I WILL KILL HER!

05:28.156 --> 05:31.262
I SLIT HER NECK!
I SMASH HER HEAD!

05:31.295 --> 05:32.632
ALL RIGHT,
THANKS FOR CALLING.

05:32.665 --> 05:34.301
KNOCK YOURSELF OUT.
BYE‐BYE.

05:34.335 --> 05:36.105
HELLO?

05:36.138 --> 05:37.709
[ SIGHS ]

05:37.742 --> 05:39.746
WELL, THAT, UH...

05:39.779 --> 05:40.748
IS THE ONE.

05:40.781 --> 05:42.519
GIN!
[ LAUGHS ]

05:42.552 --> 05:44.523
HE HUNG UP.
[ CELLPHONE CLATTERS ]

05:44.556 --> 05:46.125
HE PROBABLY
COULDN'T UNDERSTAND YOU

05:46.158 --> 05:47.562
WITH YOUR FUCKING
LAME ACCENT.

05:47.595 --> 05:50.300
OH, HE UNDERSTOOD ME.
HE'S BROKE.

05:50.333 --> 05:51.402
WHO WAS ON THE PHONE?

05:51.435 --> 05:53.139
SOMEONE'S
KIDNAPPED YOUR MOTHER.

05:53.172 --> 05:54.208
SERIOUSLY?

05:54.241 --> 05:56.713
WHO KNOWS?
ANOTHER GAME?

05:56.747 --> 05:58.082
SURE.

05:58.116 --> 06:00.487
WE ARE FIGHTING FOR THE SOULS
OF WORKERS EVERYWHERE.

06:00.521 --> 06:02.725
[ GRUNTS ]
[ SCREAMS ]

06:02.759 --> 06:04.295
[ CLANGING ]

06:04.328 --> 06:06.299
GET ME MY MONEY!

06:06.332 --> 06:10.273
[ GROANS, SOBS ]

06:10.307 --> 06:12.779
JESUS!

06:12.812 --> 06:16.787
WHAT THE HELL
IS GOING ON HERE?

06:50.688 --> 06:54.529
SO, WE PICK UP SOME MEXICAN
FARMLAND ON THE CHEAP

06:54.562 --> 06:55.731
AND MAKE A GO OF IT.

06:55.765 --> 06:57.602
[ WATER BUBBLING ]
THIS COOKIE IS AMAZING.

06:57.635 --> 06:59.973
IT'S SO SIMPLE
AND YET SO DELICIOUS.

07:00.006 --> 07:01.208
THAT'S A TERRIBLE PLAN.

07:01.242 --> 07:03.446
THE SOIL IN MEXICO
IS FULL OF PARAQUAT ‐‐

07:03.479 --> 07:04.448
MEXICAN SEWER POOP.

07:04.481 --> 07:05.985
NO ONE'S GONNA
WANT TO BUY THAT.

07:06.018 --> 07:07.956
AND ALL THE HASSLE
OF GETTING IT ACROSS THE BORDER.

07:07.989 --> 07:09.626
AND DO YOU GUYS
EVEN SPEAK SPANISH?

07:09.659 --> 07:12.030
WHAT ARE THE MARKS
ON YOUR NECK?

07:12.064 --> 07:14.001
JERKED OFF WITH A NOOSE.

07:14.034 --> 07:15.437
NICE.

07:15.470 --> 07:18.076
HEY, STONERS,
MOM EVER COME BACK?

07:18.109 --> 07:19.378
NICE HAIR.

07:19.411 --> 07:21.415
YEAH, SIMONE
AND HARMONY DID IT.

07:21.449 --> 07:22.417
AND CHECK IT OUT.

07:22.451 --> 07:24.088
WRONG EAR.

07:24.121 --> 07:25.524
FUCK! SERIOUSLY?!

07:25.558 --> 07:27.160
[ LAUGHS ]
I'M KIDDING.

07:27.194 --> 07:28.931
ASSHOLE.

07:28.964 --> 07:31.737
OH!
Doug: YOU GUYS OUGHT TO GROW IT
IN A NATIONAL PARK.

07:31.770 --> 07:33.574
ALL THE COOL KIDS ARE
DOING IT NOW, AND IT'S FREE ‐‐

07:33.607 --> 07:36.947
LIKE THE EAGLE,
GIFT WITH PURCHASE,

07:36.980 --> 07:39.251
THE NELSON MANDELA.

07:39.284 --> 07:40.921
IS THERE A NATIONAL PARK
AROUND HERE?

07:40.955 --> 07:42.558
THERE'S CLEVELAND
NATIONAL FOREST.

07:42.592 --> 07:45.296
WE'RE NOT IN OHIO, LITTLE MAN.
ARE YOU ON DRUGS?

07:45.330 --> 07:46.633
IT'S IN SAN DIEGO COUNTY.

07:46.667 --> 07:49.706
WE SHOULD GROW IN CINCINNATI
NATIONAL FOREST, SILAS.

07:49.739 --> 07:50.741
CLEVELAND.

07:50.775 --> 07:52.645
[ SPITS ]
CLEVELAND, PITTSBURGH.

07:52.679 --> 07:54.716
YOU'RE OBSESSED WITH
THE RUST BELT. WHAT IS THAT?

07:54.749 --> 07:55.985
IF MOM DOESN'T COME HOME

07:56.018 --> 07:57.487
BY THE END OF THE WEEK,
I CALL HER BEDROOM.

07:57.522 --> 08:00.093
FUCK THAT. I'M OLDER.
I GET THE ROOM.

08:00.126 --> 08:01.395
YOU VULTURES.

08:01.429 --> 08:03.333
IF NANCY
DOESN'T COME BACK,

08:03.366 --> 08:04.869
WE SHROUD THE ROOM
IN CLEAR PLASTIC

08:04.903 --> 08:06.540
AND NOTHING'S TOUCHED,
YOU HEAR ME?

08:06.573 --> 08:10.380
YOU TOUCH NOTHING IN THERE,
ANIMALS.

08:10.413 --> 08:11.683
ROCK, PAPER, SCISSORS?

08:11.717 --> 08:13.019
BEST TWO OUT OF THREE.
GO.

08:13.052 --> 08:13.987
1, 2, 3.

08:14.021 --> 08:16.526
OH, SORRY TO DISAPPOINT YOU,
BUT I'M BACK.

08:16.560 --> 08:19.164
OH. YOU'RE BACK.
SHE'S BACK.

08:19.198 --> 08:20.801
YEAH.

08:20.835 --> 08:22.839
WHAT'S WRONG
WITH YOUR NECK?

08:25.043 --> 08:27.749
[ WHISPERING ]

08:33.092 --> 08:35.397
[ SEA GULLS SQUAWKING ]

08:35.430 --> 08:36.767
[ CELLPHONE RINGING ]

08:42.310 --> 08:43.580
HELLO?

08:43.614 --> 08:45.684
Rodolfo:
I have your friend.

08:45.718 --> 08:47.822
WHAT? WHO IS THIS?
WHAT FRIEND?

08:47.855 --> 08:50.995
Your friend, Celia.
I have her.

08:51.028 --> 08:53.366
And you pay me money
or she dies.

08:53.399 --> 08:54.536
CELIA?

08:54.569 --> 08:55.971
Celia Hodes!

08:56.005 --> 08:58.911
I have kidnapped her,
and today I chop off her ear.

08:58.944 --> 09:00.915
HOW VAN GOGH.

09:00.948 --> 09:01.750
What?!

09:01.783 --> 09:04.923
You send me $40,000,
or I'll do it!

09:04.956 --> 09:07.461
[ GROANS ]
IT'S TOO EARLY FOR THIS.

09:07.494 --> 09:08.964
WE'RE REALLY NOT FRIENDS.

09:08.997 --> 09:10.868
Okay, thirty‐thou‐‐

09:12.839 --> 09:15.644
HEY, YOU UP?
YOU AWAKE?

09:15.678 --> 09:17.247
HEARD YOUR CELLPHONE RING,
SO ‐‐

09:17.280 --> 09:19.586
ANDY, I NEED TO SLEEP.

09:19.619 --> 09:20.988
NANCE, I GOT A PLAN.

09:21.021 --> 09:22.224
THAT'S NICE.

09:22.257 --> 09:24.763
WE SHOULD FLEE.

09:25.931 --> 09:27.635
THAT'S MY PLAN ‐‐
FLEEING.

09:27.668 --> 09:30.541
WE CAN'T FLEE.
WHY NOT?

09:30.574 --> 09:33.747
IT'S THE MEXICAN MAFIA.
THERE'S NOWHERE TO GO.

09:33.781 --> 09:35.216
YEAH?
WHAT ARE YOU GONNA DO?

09:35.250 --> 09:38.256
SIT AROUND, WAIT FOR THEM
TO KILL US? YOU? YOU AND US?

09:38.289 --> 09:41.395
IT'S ONLY A MATTER OF TIME,
NANCE.

09:41.429 --> 09:42.932
YOU FINKED, AND THEY KNOW IT,
DON'T THEY?

09:42.965 --> 09:44.736
AND NOW THEY'RE JUST PLAYING
WITH YOU.

09:44.769 --> 09:47.240
YOU'RE A CAT TOY,
AND THEY'RE CATS ‐‐

09:47.274 --> 09:49.612
MEXICAN CATS, GATOS.

09:49.646 --> 09:50.614
[ MOANS ]

09:50.648 --> 09:53.352
PLEASE, LET ME SLEEP.
NO.

09:53.386 --> 09:57.260
TIME TO GET UP, 'CAUSE I'VE GOT
A WHOLE PLAN WORKED OUT.

09:59.264 --> 10:00.935
WE'RE GOING TO DENMARK.

10:02.337 --> 10:05.945
THE MEXICAN MAFIA'S
NOT GONNA FIND US IN COPENHAGEN.

10:05.978 --> 10:09.619
RIGHT? IT'S SUPPOSED TO BE
WONDERFUL THERE.

10:09.652 --> 10:13.927
WONDERFUL, WONDERFUL.
AND I LOVE YOU.

10:13.961 --> 10:15.931
[ SIGHS ]

10:15.965 --> 10:17.367
Andy...

10:20.306 --> 10:22.210
...I'm pregnant.

10:25.016 --> 10:27.020
I need to sleep.

10:28.724 --> 10:32.063
YOU'RE ‐‐
WOW, THAT'S...

10:32.097 --> 10:34.101
[ LAUGHS ]

10:36.105 --> 10:37.742
ANDY, WAIT. WHAT?

10:37.775 --> 10:38.911
NO, NO, GET SOME SLEEP.

10:38.944 --> 10:42.752
BUT, UM...
Shh,
I'LL TALK TO YOU LATER.

10:42.785 --> 10:45.658
[ DOOR CLOSES ]
[ SIGHS ]

10:47.628 --> 10:49.833
[ CELLPHONE RINGING ]

10:51.937 --> 10:52.672
WHAT?

10:52.705 --> 10:54.208
Cesar: Nancy.

10:54.241 --> 10:55.243
OH, HI, CESAR.

10:55.276 --> 10:56.913
I'm giving you
an address.

10:56.947 --> 11:00.220
You will be there
at 2:00 p. m.

11:09.973 --> 11:12.310
DID YOU GET TO
THE ANAL‐RAPE SCENE YET?

11:12.344 --> 11:13.780
THANKS FOR RUINING IT
FOR ME.

11:13.814 --> 11:15.483
DON'T WORRY.
THERE'S TWO.

11:15.518 --> 11:17.320
I DON'T THINK
I'M GONNA FINISH THIS.

11:22.698 --> 11:25.504
HELLO, SHANE.
DOING YOUR READING?

11:25.538 --> 11:27.508
MR. SANDUSKY, UH...

11:27.542 --> 11:29.478
DID YOU ACTUALLY READ
"THE KITE RUNNER"

11:29.512 --> 11:30.648
BEFORE YOU ASSIGNED IT?

11:30.681 --> 11:32.919
I DID. I THOUGHT YOU GUYS
COULD HANDLE IT.

11:32.952 --> 11:34.923
CAN YOU HANDLE IT,
SHANE?

11:34.956 --> 11:36.425
'CAUSE IT SEEMS
LIKE YOU CAN HANDLE A LOT.

11:36.458 --> 11:37.528
YOU'RE SUCH A MULTITASKER.

11:37.562 --> 11:39.197
I DON'T KNOW
WHAT YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT.

11:39.231 --> 11:40.701
SURE, YOU DO.

11:40.734 --> 11:42.605
NO, I DON'T.

11:42.638 --> 11:45.443
SHANE, I HAVE 23 PAPERS
TO GRADE TONIGHT.

11:45.476 --> 11:46.980
THEY'RE ALL ON ANNE FRANK.

11:47.013 --> 11:48.684
DO YOU KNOW
HOW DEPRESSING THAT IS?

11:48.717 --> 11:50.754
YOU PICK
REALLY SAD BOOKS.

11:50.788 --> 11:52.592
WHICH IS WHY
I NEED SOME POT.

11:52.625 --> 11:54.629
PLUS, YOU PEOPLE
CAN'T WRITE FOR SHIT.

11:54.662 --> 11:55.764
THAT'S EVEN SADDER.

11:55.798 --> 11:57.467
SHOULDN'T THAT BE
"MORE SAD"?

11:57.500 --> 11:59.806
TELL ME, SMARTASS,

11:59.839 --> 12:02.043
IF I WERE TO CONFISCATE
YOUR BAG RIGHT NOW

12:02.077 --> 12:04.348
AND GO THROUGH IT
WITH PRINCIPAL ROWAN,

12:04.381 --> 12:06.285
WHAT WOULD WE FIND?

12:08.489 --> 12:10.159
A CURE FOR DEPRESSION?

12:13.934 --> 12:16.238
HE ALWAYS WORE WIFE BEATERS
OR TANK TOPS.

12:16.272 --> 12:19.812
HE HAD A BEARD.
I LIKE GUYS WITH BEARDS.

12:19.846 --> 12:24.021
YOU SAW NO ONE ELSE
THE ENTIRE TIME?

12:24.054 --> 12:25.858
NO BIG BOSS?

12:25.891 --> 12:29.532
NO, JUST THE CUTE ONE
WITH THE BEARD.

12:29.565 --> 12:32.003
[ INTERCOM BEEPS ]

12:32.037 --> 12:35.009
Man: Hey, Cap, there's a guy
on line one calling from Mexico.

12:35.043 --> 12:36.613
He's demanding to talk to you.

12:36.646 --> 12:40.521
TRACE IT.
COULD BE RELATED.

12:40.554 --> 12:44.027
YEAH.

12:45.864 --> 12:48.002
LET ME GET THIS STRAIGHT ‐‐

12:48.035 --> 12:51.041
YOU WANT A RANSOM
FOR CELIA HODES?

12:52.511 --> 12:56.118
GO FUCK YOURSELF!

12:57.888 --> 13:00.928
CANCEL THE TRACE.
IT'S BULLSHIT.

13:00.961 --> 13:02.932
Silas:
SEE? RIGHT HERE?

13:02.965 --> 13:05.971
THAT'S A SIX‐HOUR HIKE,
AND THERE ARE NO ROADS UP THERE.

13:06.005 --> 13:08.175
I THINK
WE SHOULD CHECK IT OUT.

13:08.209 --> 13:09.512
ANDY?

13:09.545 --> 13:12.985
OH...YEAH.
IT'S ‐‐ SURE.

13:13.019 --> 13:14.689
IT'S GONNA BE
A LOT TO CARRY.

13:14.722 --> 13:16.526
WE'RE GONNA NEED TO PACK OUT
ALL THE PLANTS,

13:16.559 --> 13:17.962
ADVANCED NUTRIENTS.

13:17.995 --> 13:21.636
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]
WE NEED TUBING
FOR A WATER SYSTEM.

13:21.670 --> 13:23.272
HELLO?

13:23.306 --> 13:25.109
WHO?

13:25.143 --> 13:26.946
CELIA?

13:26.980 --> 13:30.888
THAT CUNT CAN LICK MY BALLS.
TELL HER I SAID HI.

13:30.921 --> 13:32.090
[ CELLPHONE CLOSES ]

13:32.123 --> 13:34.061
SO, TUBING, PLANTS ‐‐
WHAT ELSE?

13:34.094 --> 13:36.766
I DON'T REMEMBER
INVITING YOU INTO THIS, DOUG.

13:36.800 --> 13:38.870
COME ON,
I'M AN EXTRA PACK MULE.

13:38.904 --> 13:40.974
AND I'M BORED,
AND I'M GOOD AT THIS.

13:41.008 --> 13:43.379
I USED TO TAKE MY FAMILY
CAMPING EVERY YEAR.

13:43.412 --> 13:44.682
AND ANDY'S GONE CATATONIC,

13:44.716 --> 13:46.920
SO, YOU KNOW, AT LEAST
YOU COULD CHAT WITH ME.

13:46.953 --> 13:50.761
[ CELLPHONE RINGING ]
ANDY, BUDDY, DOING OKAY?

13:50.794 --> 13:52.297
FINE.
I'M DOING FINE.

13:52.330 --> 13:54.167
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

13:54.201 --> 13:55.604
HELLO.

13:55.637 --> 13:58.009
YEAH, I KNOW CELIA.

13:59.912 --> 14:02.350
[ CHUCKLES ]
WELL, WE'RE ALL GONNA DIE.

14:02.384 --> 14:04.154
WHAT'S IT MEAN, ANYWAY?
LIFE IS CHEAP.

14:04.187 --> 14:07.528
PEOPLE DIE,
AND PEOPLE HAVE BABIES.

14:07.561 --> 14:09.197
EVERY DAY,
THEY'RE HAVING BABIES.

14:09.231 --> 14:11.970
WHAT'S WITH THAT,
KIDNAPPER MAN?

14:12.003 --> 14:14.876
I MEAN, WOMEN IN THEIR 40s
ARE HAVING BABIES?

14:14.909 --> 14:17.982
DOESN'T THAT SEEM WEIRD
TO YOU?

14:18.015 --> 14:21.656
WHAT? NO.
I'M NOT GONNA PAY THE RANSOM.

14:21.689 --> 14:24.796
HELLO?

14:24.829 --> 14:26.498
RUDE.

14:28.436 --> 14:32.578
ANDY,
WHO'S HAVING A BABY?

14:32.611 --> 14:34.181
[ CHUCKLES ]

14:34.214 --> 14:35.918
NO ONE?

14:35.951 --> 14:38.155
AND I'M IN THE Z's.

14:38.189 --> 14:40.026
NO ONE?

14:40.059 --> 14:42.330
[ SIGHS ] DO YOU HAVE
A FACEBOOK PAGE?

14:42.363 --> 14:44.635
MAYBE YOU HAVE
SOME FRIENDS THERE?

14:44.669 --> 14:46.973
I DON'T HAVE
A FACEBOOK PAGE.

14:47.006 --> 14:50.146
CLEARLY, THAT WOULD BE
A WASTE OF TIME.

14:51.181 --> 14:54.655
WHAT ARE PEOPLE SAYING
WHEN YOU CALL?

14:54.689 --> 14:56.191
AH, THAT THE ECONOMY'S BAD,

14:56.225 --> 14:58.930
THAT YOU HAVEN'T TALKED
FOR A WHILE.

14:58.964 --> 15:01.603
AND MANY PEOPLE SAID
TO SAY HELLO.

15:01.636 --> 15:05.042
YOU'RE JUST
TRYING TO BE NICE.

15:05.076 --> 15:06.713
EVERYBODY HATES ME.

15:06.746 --> 15:08.482
VERY MUCH.

15:10.554 --> 15:12.090
[ SIGHS ]

15:12.123 --> 15:14.294
DID YOU PUT SOMETHING
ON THOSE SCRATCHES,

15:14.327 --> 15:15.998
LIKE...NEOSPORIN?

15:16.031 --> 15:18.570
EH. I'M OKAY.

15:18.603 --> 15:20.974
NO, YOU'RE NOT.

15:21.008 --> 15:24.014
WHY DO YOU LET HER
DO THAT TO YOU?

15:25.617 --> 15:27.053
SHE'S ABUSIVE.

15:27.086 --> 15:30.293
ROBERTO, YOU DO NOT
HAVE TO TAKE THIS.

15:30.326 --> 15:31.328
RODOLFO.

15:31.361 --> 15:37.273
AND HOW OFTEN DOES
SHE HIT YOU...RODOLFO?

15:37.307 --> 15:39.077
I DON'T KNOW.

15:39.111 --> 15:41.215
SHE DOESN'T MEAN
TO HURT ME.

15:41.248 --> 15:45.022
I JUST ‐‐
I MAKE HER SO MAD SOMETI‐‐

15:45.056 --> 15:47.193
WHAT THE HELL
IS GOING ON IN HERE?!

15:47.227 --> 15:49.030
I'M TRYING TO MAKE
THE PHONE CALLS, QUINN,

15:49.064 --> 15:50.166
BUT NOBODY'S PAYING.

15:50.199 --> 15:52.872
[ SIGHS ]
FINE. THEN FUCK IT.

15:52.905 --> 15:55.744
WE'LL KILL HER
AND SELL HER ORGANS, OKAY?

15:55.777 --> 15:59.251
LET'S GO HAVE SEX.

16:04.529 --> 16:08.035
[ HORNS HONKING ]

16:18.055 --> 16:20.694
ENTONCES, DOCTOR,
vHACIENDO ESTAS PRUEBAS

16:20.727 --> 16:22.698
VAMOS A OBTENER
LA PATERNIDAD

16:22.731 --> 16:24.836
Y EL SEXO DEL BEBé?

16:24.869 --> 16:26.371
Sí, Y TAMBIéN
PODRíAMOS DETECTAR

16:26.405 --> 16:27.641
CUALQUIER DESORDEN
DE CROMOSOMAS O GENéTICO,

16:27.675 --> 16:31.381
SíNDROME DE DOWN,
TRISOMíA 13, TRISOMíA 18,

16:31.415 --> 16:34.187
SíNDROME DE TURNER,
SíNDROME KLINEFELTER.

16:34.221 --> 16:36.158
LOS RESULTADOS
ESTARáN DISPONIBLES

16:36.191 --> 16:37.126
EN SIETE O DIEZ DíAS.

16:37.160 --> 16:38.997
Cesar:
vLOS PODEMOS TENER ANTES?

16:39.030 --> 16:41.101
NECESITAMOS TIEMPO
PARA CULTIVAR LAS CéLULAS

16:41.134 --> 16:43.005
DE LA PLACENTA
PARA EL ANáLISIS.

16:43.038 --> 16:45.142
vY ESTE PROCEDIMIENTO
TIENE ALGúN RIESGO?

16:45.176 --> 16:47.146
SIEMPRE SE CORREN RIESGOS
EN ESTE TIPO DE COSAS,

16:47.180 --> 16:48.917
PERO EL PORCENTAJE
ES MUY BAJO.

16:48.950 --> 16:50.219
vTú QUé PIENSAS, CESAR?

16:50.253 --> 16:52.558
NECESITAMOS
LA INFORMACIóN,

16:52.591 --> 16:55.129
COMO DICE EL DOCTOR,
EL RIESGO ES MUY BAJO.

16:55.162 --> 16:57.668
[ SIGHS ]
MUY BIEN.

16:57.701 --> 17:00.072
ENTONCES HACEMOS LA PRUEBA.

17:00.106 --> 17:01.308
POR FAVOR, MIRABEL,

17:01.341 --> 17:03.312
PREPARA A LA SRA. GONZALES
PARA UN ULTRASONIDO,

17:03.345 --> 17:05.116
VAMOS A VER
SI VAMOS A ENTRAR

17:05.149 --> 17:06.786
A TRAVéS DE LA CéRVIX
O EL ESTóMAGO.

17:06.819 --> 17:08.255
[ Mumbling ]
HELLO?

17:08.289 --> 17:11.094
CAN SOMEONE PLEASE TELL ME
WHAT'S GOING ON?

17:11.128 --> 17:12.463
vHA FIRMADO LA SEÑORA
LOS PAPELES

17:12.497 --> 17:14.034
DANDO SU CONSENTIMIENTO
PARA LA EXAMEN?

17:14.067 --> 17:15.837
NO, AHORA LO HARá.

17:15.871 --> 17:18.108
NANCY, YOU NEED TO SIGN
THESE FORMS.

17:18.142 --> 17:19.779
WHAT AM I SIGNING?

17:19.812 --> 17:22.785
IT'S A CONSENT
FOR A CVS PROCEDURE.

17:22.818 --> 17:25.591
I DON'T EVEN KNOW
WHAT THAT IS.

17:25.624 --> 17:27.995
I CAN'T UNDERSTAND
WHAT THE DOCTOR IS SAYING.

17:28.028 --> 17:32.203
THIS IS JU‐‐ UH...

17:32.237 --> 17:34.441
FORGET IT.
I'M GOING HOME.

17:34.474 --> 17:37.815
POR FAVOR NOS PERMITEN
UN MOMENTO.

17:37.848 --> 17:39.184
NECESITO HABLAR CON...

17:39.217 --> 17:42.123
LA SRA. GONZALES.

17:42.156 --> 17:45.029
DESPUéS HACEMOS LA PRUEBA,
vSí? POR FAVOR.

17:45.062 --> 17:46.398
CLARO.

17:48.469 --> 17:50.406
SEÑORA GONZALEZ?

17:51.943 --> 17:53.713
I'M NOT COMFORTABLE
WITH THIS.

17:53.747 --> 17:55.249
I DON'T EVEN KNOW
WHERE I AM.

17:55.283 --> 17:58.022
IT'S LIKE I'VE BEEN SUCKED UP
INTO THE ALIEN CRAFT

17:58.055 --> 17:59.291
AND I'M BEING PROBED.

17:59.324 --> 18:01.629
WHERE ARE MY CLOTHES?
CAN SOMEONE PLEASE BRING ME ‐‐

18:01.663 --> 18:03.499
YOU HAVE NO IDEA, DO YOU?

18:07.106 --> 18:09.077
THIS IS YOUR BABY.

18:09.110 --> 18:11.916
I...TOTALLY UNDERSTAND
IF YOU NEED PROOF.

18:11.950 --> 18:15.991
WHY DON'T WE MAKE AN APPOINTMENT
WITH A DOCTOR IN REN MAR,

18:16.024 --> 18:17.561
SOMEONE
WHO SPEAKS ENGLISH,

18:17.594 --> 18:20.066
ACTUALLY ADDRESSES ME
LIKE I'M A HUMAN BEING?

18:20.099 --> 18:21.869
WE'LL GO TOGETHER.
WE'LL GET LUNCH AFTER.

18:21.903 --> 18:22.905
HOW ABOUT THAT?

18:22.938 --> 18:24.274
HOW ABOUT THAT?

18:24.307 --> 18:27.447
HOW ABOUT YOU'RE LAZARUS?

18:29.284 --> 18:31.221
RISEN FROM THE DEAD.

18:31.254 --> 18:33.526
AND YOU WILL LIE BACK,
OPEN YOUR LEGS,

18:33.560 --> 18:37.300
AND SHOW DR. BRISA,
THE DOCTOR I'VE CHOSEN,

18:37.333 --> 18:41.909
THAT IN YOUR FLAT STOMACH,
THERE IS A BABY

18:41.943 --> 18:43.780
THAT IS BOTH MALE
AND MINE.

18:43.813 --> 18:45.082
I WANT TO GO HOME.

18:45.116 --> 18:49.324
IF YOU WANT TO GO HOME,
CESAR WILL TAKE YOU.

18:49.357 --> 18:54.234
YOU WANT TO GO?
GO.

19:03.452 --> 19:06.559
[ SIGHS ]

19:11.301 --> 19:12.771
[ DOOR OPENS, CLOSES ]

19:12.805 --> 19:14.240
DOCTOR.

19:14.274 --> 19:16.478
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATION
IN SPANISH ]

19:23.827 --> 19:26.031
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

19:26.064 --> 19:29.404
[ PLASTIC SNAPS ]

19:34.882 --> 19:36.485
THATWAS HUMILIATING.

19:36.519 --> 19:37.955
Rodolfo:
I KNOW. I‐I'M SORRY.

19:37.988 --> 19:39.124
I COULD NOT UNTIE YOU.

19:39.157 --> 19:41.428
YOU ARE SUPPOSED TO WIPE
FRONT TO BACK.

19:41.461 --> 19:42.965
IF I GET
SOME KIND OF INFECTION ‐‐

19:42.998 --> 19:45.302
IT WASN'T EXACTLY
A THRILL FOR ME, OKAY?

19:45.336 --> 19:47.273
JUST TIE HER BACK INTO THE CHAIR
AND WASH YOUR HANDS, RODOLFO.

19:47.306 --> 19:49.979
IS THIS REALLY
NECESSARY?

19:50.012 --> 19:52.450
COME ON, QUINN.
ENOUGH IS ENOUGH.

19:52.483 --> 19:57.393
YOU'VE PROVEN YOUR POINT.
YOU'RE ANGRY.

19:57.427 --> 19:59.732
AND I HAVE TO MAKE AMENDS
FOR MY MANY MISTAKES,

19:59.765 --> 20:01.168
SO HERE IS MY PROPOSAL.

20:01.201 --> 20:03.707
AS WE ALL KNOW NOW,
I AM BROKE.

20:03.740 --> 20:07.514
BUT THAT DOESN'T MEAN I CAN'T
CHARGE, ON MY CREDIT CARD ‐‐

20:07.548 --> 20:11.421
AND WORRY ABOUT IT LATER ‐‐
A WEEK AT A SPA.

20:11.455 --> 20:15.129
LET'S JUST FORGET
ALL OF THIS SILLINESS

20:15.162 --> 20:19.605
AND GO HAVE
REHYDRATING FACIALS.

20:19.638 --> 20:23.178
YOU LOOK A LITTLE DRY THERE,
HONEY.

20:23.212 --> 20:26.552
[ CHUCKLES ]

20:26.586 --> 20:27.320
OH.

20:27.353 --> 20:30.092
THEY'RE GONNA
SAW YOU OPEN, MOM.

20:30.126 --> 20:32.931
THEY'RE GONNA SLICE OUT
YOUR CORNEAS,

20:32.965 --> 20:34.902
YOUR KIDNEYS, YOUR LUNGS.

20:34.935 --> 20:37.741
THEY PROBABLY WON'T BE
TOO INTERESTED IN YOUR LIVER,

20:37.775 --> 20:39.077
CONSIDERING YOUR PAST.

20:39.110 --> 20:42.083
BUT BY THE TIME
THEY'RE THROUGH

20:42.116 --> 20:44.354
PUTTING YOU INTO A DOZEN
IGLOO COOLERS

20:44.387 --> 20:46.358
AND SHIPPING YOU OFF
TO THE BLACK MARKET,

20:46.391 --> 20:49.364
YOU SHOULD NET ME
ABOUT $100K.

20:50.499 --> 20:53.172
AND THEN I'LL TOAST
YOUR MEMORY...

20:53.205 --> 20:55.276
FROM THE DECK
OF MY BEACH HOUSE.

20:56.311 --> 20:58.449
OH, HONEY.

20:58.482 --> 21:02.356
YOU CAN'T BUY A BEACH HOUSE
FOR $100K.

21:02.390 --> 21:04.194
AND WHEN THEY CUT OUT
YOUR HEART, MOM,

21:04.227 --> 21:06.031
I THINK
I WANT TO BE THERE...

21:06.064 --> 21:08.435
JUST TO CONFIRM
THAT YOU HAD ONE.

21:08.469 --> 21:09.337
JESUS.

21:09.370 --> 21:13.479
I SURVIVED CANCER
AND REHAB FOR THIS.

21:13.513 --> 21:16.351
FUCK IT.
CAN I HAVE A DRINK?

21:16.384 --> 21:17.654
YOU HAD CANCER?

21:17.688 --> 21:21.027
DON'T YOU DARE START
FEELING SORRY FOR HER.
Shh.

21:21.061 --> 21:22.497
DID YOU HAVE CHEMO?

21:22.531 --> 21:24.502
SURE ‐‐
CHEMO, RADIATION.

21:24.535 --> 21:26.506
DO YOU HAVE ANY MORE
OF THAT STUFF YOU GAVE ME

21:26.539 --> 21:28.375
THAT MADE ME SLEEP ‐‐
I'LL TAKE SOME OF THAT.

21:28.408 --> 21:30.547
QUINN, THEY WILL NOT
TAKE HER ORGANS.

21:30.580 --> 21:31.348
WHAT?

21:31.381 --> 21:34.053
SHE HAD RADIATION,
CHEMO.

21:34.087 --> 21:36.258
AND A DOUBLE MASTECTOMY.

21:36.291 --> 21:37.360
THEY'RE GOING TO
KNOW THIS

21:37.393 --> 21:39.063
THE MOMENT
THEY OPEN HER SHIRT.

21:39.097 --> 21:42.871
QUINN, IT'S NO GOOD.

21:42.905 --> 21:45.442
YOU FUCKING BITCH!

21:46.712 --> 21:48.148
[ SCREAMING ]

21:48.182 --> 21:50.720
QUINN!
ENOUGH! ENOUGH!

21:51.689 --> 21:54.060
GET OUT! OUT!

21:54.093 --> 21:56.231
OUT OF MY LIFE!
OUT OF MY TENT!

21:56.264 --> 21:58.770
YOU ARE A MEAN PERSON!

22:03.212 --> 22:04.748
[ CHUCKLES ]

22:04.782 --> 22:07.588
HAVE FUN TOGETHER.

22:08.890 --> 22:11.596
[ CRYING ]

22:14.400 --> 22:16.973
OH, GOOD CHRIST.

22:17.006 --> 22:19.177
WATCH OUT! INCOMING! TAKE COVER!
[ IMITATES EXPLOSION ]

22:19.210 --> 22:21.414
AAH, MY EYES! MY EYES!
I CAN'T SEE!

22:21.448 --> 22:23.352
DOUG, IF YOU DON'T HELP,
YOU CAN'T COME.

22:23.385 --> 22:25.624
WHY CAN'T WE JUST BUY
SOME NEW STUFF?

22:25.657 --> 22:29.030
THERE WAS A DEAD MOUSE
IN THAT BACKPACK.

22:29.063 --> 22:30.199
HEY.

22:30.232 --> 22:31.434
HEY, KID.

22:31.468 --> 22:32.604
WHAT'S WRONG
WITH UNCLE ANDY?

22:32.638 --> 22:35.510
HE'S BAKING BANANA BREAD,
LIKE 13 OF THEM.

22:35.544 --> 22:37.413
OH, HE'S FREAKING OUT
'CAUSE YOUR MOM'S PREGNANT.

22:38.683 --> 22:39.585
EXCUSE ME?

22:39.618 --> 22:41.589
[ Imitating soldier ]
KNOCKED UP, PRIVATE!

22:41.622 --> 22:44.427
BABY ON BOARD!
MUFFIN IN THE MUFF! GRR!

22:44.460 --> 22:47.433
YOU'RE JUST AN IDIOT,
YOU KNOW THAT?

22:47.466 --> 22:50.540
[ Normal voice ] WHAT? WHAT?
I DIDN'T KNOCK HER UP.

22:52.376 --> 22:54.013
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

22:54.047 --> 22:57.554
MMM,
SOMETHING SMELLS AMAZING.

22:57.588 --> 22:59.224
THEY SAY
THAT PREGNANT WOMEN

22:59.257 --> 23:00.961
HAVE A HEIGHTENED SENSE
OF SMELL.

23:00.994 --> 23:02.363
ARE YOU TALKING TO ME?

23:02.396 --> 23:04.568
WELL,
I'VE BEEN THINKING.

23:04.602 --> 23:06.939
JUST BECAUSE YOU'VE BEEN
A SLUTTY,

23:06.973 --> 23:09.444
IRRESPONSIBLE,
SLUTTY SLUT

23:09.477 --> 23:13.018
WHO HAD UNPROTECTED SEX
WITH A MEXICAN GANGSTER,

23:13.051 --> 23:15.256
THAT DOESN'T MEAN
THAT WE CAN'T BE FRIENDS, RIGHT?

23:15.289 --> 23:16.491
DID YOU WANT TO LICK
THE SPATULA?

23:16.525 --> 23:18.963
I NEED TO
ASK YOU A FAVOR.

23:18.997 --> 23:20.533
OF COURSE YOU DO.

23:20.567 --> 23:22.537
I NEED YOU TO TAKE SHANE
UP TO MY SISTER'S

23:22.571 --> 23:23.673
IN THE OAKLAND HOUSE.

23:23.706 --> 23:26.512
JILL PRICE‐GRAY, WITH A HYPHEN?
BITCH FACE?

23:26.545 --> 23:28.516
IT'S THE LESSER
OF TWO EVILS.

23:28.549 --> 23:30.787
I'LL HAVE TO CHECK
MY SCHEDULE.

23:33.492 --> 23:34.595
I LOVE YOU, TOO,
YOU KNOW.

23:34.628 --> 23:36.364
YEAH,
BUT NOT IN THE GOOD WAY.

23:36.398 --> 23:37.834
Shane:
YOU'RE FULL OF SHIT.

23:37.868 --> 23:39.237
ASK HER YOURSELF.

23:39.270 --> 23:40.840
YOU'RE PREGNANT?

23:42.109 --> 23:43.613
YES.

23:43.646 --> 23:45.049
SEE?

23:45.082 --> 23:46.384
YOU'VE GOT
A BIG MOUTH.

23:46.418 --> 23:47.521
YOU'VE GOT A BIG BABY.

23:47.554 --> 23:48.690
AND YOU'RE HOW OLD?

23:48.723 --> 23:51.428
WOMEN MY AGE
HAVE BABIES, SHANE.

23:51.461 --> 23:52.496
SO, WHEN'S THE ABORTION?

23:52.531 --> 23:55.837
I'M HAVING THE BABY,
SILAS.

23:55.870 --> 23:59.712
Andy: COME ON, IT'S A NEW LIFE,
IT'S A NEW SIBLING FOR YOU GUYS.

23:59.745 --> 24:02.383
IT'S THE KEY TO KEEPING
HER MEXICAN BOYFRIEND

24:02.416 --> 24:03.653
FROM MURDERING US ALL,

24:03.686 --> 24:06.559
AT LEAST UNTIL SHE POPS,
AND THEN WE FLEE TO DENMARK.

24:06.592 --> 24:09.297
DAD WOULD BE SO PROUD.

24:09.330 --> 24:10.600
[ SIGHS ]

24:10.634 --> 24:13.706
SHANE, TOMORROW ANDY'S GOING TO
TAKE YOU UP TO OAKLAND

24:13.740 --> 24:15.409
TO STAY WITH MY SISTER
FOR A WHILE ‐‐

24:15.442 --> 24:17.279
YOUR AUNT JILL.

24:17.313 --> 24:18.950
YOU REMEMBER AUNT JILL.

24:18.983 --> 24:20.987
FUCK...THAT.

24:21.021 --> 24:23.626
WAIT, NO. ANDY'S COMING
TO THE FOREST WITH ME AND DOUG.

24:23.660 --> 24:25.930
IT'S FOR YOUR OWN SAFETY,
AND THAT'S THE END OF IT.

24:25.964 --> 24:27.066
YOU'RE GOING.

24:27.099 --> 24:28.970
YOUR LITTLE CAMPING TRIP
WITH ANDY WILL HAVE TO WAIT.

24:29.003 --> 24:31.207
IT'S NOT A LITTLE CAMPING TRIP.
IT'S BUSINESS.

24:31.241 --> 24:32.711
I GOT TO GET MY CLONES
IN THE GROUND.

24:32.744 --> 24:33.846
WHAT A BUNCH OF BULLSHIT!

24:33.880 --> 24:35.817
HE STAYS,
I GET SENT TO OAKLAND?!

24:35.850 --> 24:36.986
FORGET IT!

24:37.019 --> 24:38.556
YOU'RE RIGHT. YOU KNOW WHAT?
TAKE THEM BOTH TO JILL'S.

24:38.589 --> 24:41.328
NO WAY! I'M NOT JUST SOME KID
YOU CAN SEND TO HIS ROOM!

24:41.361 --> 24:43.131
OH, AND I AM?!
FUCK YOU!

24:43.165 --> 24:44.167
YOU TOTALLY ARE.
WHAT?

24:44.200 --> 24:45.469
YOU GET ONE PUBE,
YOU THINK YOU'RE A GROWN‐UP?

24:45.503 --> 24:47.473
JUST DEAL.
[ GRUNTS ]

24:47.507 --> 24:48.676
SHANE.
HEY, HEY, HEY!

24:48.710 --> 24:50.212
I'M BAKING IN HERE!
SILAS!

24:50.245 --> 24:51.682
AAH!

24:51.716 --> 24:53.385
DON'T.
ANDY, DO SOMETHING.

24:53.418 --> 24:55.389
WHAT?
I GOT TO CHECK THE BREAD.
STOP IT!

24:55.422 --> 24:57.026
I'VE GOT AN AFRO DOWN THERE,
YOU ASSHOLE!

24:57.059 --> 24:59.230
STOP IT!
YEAH,
SURROUNDING YOUR PUSSY.

24:59.263 --> 25:00.567
GORGEOUS.

25:02.436 --> 25:04.173
GOD DAMN IT,
I SAID STOP!

25:04.207 --> 25:05.877
[ CLANGS ]

25:05.910 --> 25:09.250
HOT! HOT!

25:09.283 --> 25:11.421
MY BEAUTIFUL LOAF.

25:11.454 --> 25:13.626
YOU RUIN EVERYTHING
YOU TOUCH!

25:13.659 --> 25:15.029
[ BOTH GRUNTING ]

25:15.062 --> 25:16.364
YEAH, YOU BETTER RUN!

25:16.398 --> 25:17.768
FUCK YOU!

25:22.176 --> 25:24.480
